com.ibm.zrl.idmx.tests.idmx
Class TestProof

java.lang.Object
  junit.framework.Assert
      junit.framework.TestCase
          com.ibm.zrl.idmx.tests.idmx.TestProof
All Implemented Interfaces:
junit.framework.Test
public class TestProof
extends junit.framework.TestCase

Testing show-proofs. For each test there is first a specification created. Using the specification the prover creates the proof and serializes it. The verifier uses the specification and the proof and verifies the given statement.
